msgstr "Beschreibung"

#: ../../content/index.rst:20
msgid ""
"This package brings the functionality to automatically create a ticket "
"with configurable parameters to a freely chooseable point in time in "
"relation to an appointment."
msgstr ""
"Dieses Paket bringt die Funktionalität mit, automatisch ein Ticket mit "
"konfigurierbaren Parametern zu einem frei wählbaren Zeitpunkt in Bezug auf "
"einen Termin zu erstellen."

#: ../../content/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"Ticket Creation is initiated in the AppointmentEdit mask under the "
"section 'Ticket Creation'. A point in time relative to the appointment, "
"as well as ticket data can be configured. Recurring appointments are "
"supported."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/index.rst:24
msgid "The feature as of now does not support dynamic fields of type database."
msgstr ""

